{"tid":981820,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"迪帥哥要你睇到我最終勝利~~✋🏻","createTime":"2019-01-14T14:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T00:31:53.000Z","uid":294,"like":127,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"1aab04b9d70d72f3a09e3a1af9d53ed1594b24b9","tid":981820,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T14:57:26.000Z","msg":"我有我撲法怕誰太埋四連發<br />\n撲也有腳法永未折服拒絕高壓<br />\n永遠有似熱刺未試驗過未怕黑<br />\nGea Gea Gea~<br />\n<br />\n我有我性格拒絕去皇變垃圾<br />\n個老闆太廢我沒有25圖衰格<br />\n到老無態了怕比fan屎恐嚇<br />\n永遠有似熱刺未試驗過未怕黑<br />\nGea Gea Gea~<br />\n<br />\n喂你MMA咪撚咁小器 射中雙位都不過我手臂<br />\n上季這雙手於險惡化解阿妓<br />\n撲高空波封單刀阻止你 阿里孫興慜傾你請爭氣<br />\n迪帥哥要你睇到我最終勝利&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n傾好廢 射門 喂喂喂<br />\nSon好廢 射門 喂喂喂<br />\n不枉費敢摩考我幾高修為 (無多啲靚波我點衰俾你睇）<br />\n普巴貴? 妙傳 喂喂喂<br />\n福仔廢? 入球 喂喂喂<br />\n鍾斯廢! 即管考我怎麼解圍<br />\n我擋過的靚波已經太多太多 對手記得踢波咪講咁多放馬過嚟"},{"pid":"eb8e2afd7642816929582ff4894db2f1783a0812","tid":981820,"uid":294,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T14:58:40.000Z","msg":"*Gea 讀音 Hea ar"},{"pid":"bc19d8371cc3ddd4aa980ac7ff79aba49232730f","tid":981820,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T14:59:39.000Z","msg":"第二段copy 多左句<br />\n<br />\n<del>永遠有似熱刺未試驗過未怕黑</del>"},{"pid":"b32ddf8c0dd182970053abd30f18a620a7015399","tid":981820,"uid":294,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:04:01.000Z","msg":"原曲<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lZLlVm9C1nY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlZLlVm9C1nY&d=Kj2VNr%2Fz%2FzEZPka8Htoob26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=3a04a185\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lZLlVm9C1nY</a>"},{"pid":"f4e0348735b9ab6fcc79e84bfaf1b506dab5fe8a","tid":981820,"uid":294,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T15:05:48.000Z","msg":"有無人唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 韓費彈狗黑b?"},{"pid":"78d8d9e2d487996391ce624e41bcfbf791a12529","tid":981820,"uid":37747,"like":16,"dislike"